# Privacy Policy  
**Last Updated: January 23, 2025**  

## Introduction  
Welcome to **Study Buddy**, an educational application developed by BevyLabs. This privacy policy explains our commitment to protecting your privacy while using our app.  

---

## 1. Information We Do Not Collect  
Our app operates entirely offline and does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. We do not:  

- Collect personal identification information  
- Track user behavior or analytics  
- Store any images processed through the app  
- Share any data with third parties  
- Use cookies or tracking technologies  

---

## 2. Use of the App  
Our app requires the following permissions:  

- **Camera access**: To capture images of educational text  
- **Gallery access**: To select existing images of educational text  

These permissions are used solely for:  

- Processing educational text images locally on your device  
- Generating practice questions using Google Gemini API  
- Creating interactive learning materials  

All image processing and question generation occurs locally on your device. Images are not stored or transmitted to external servers.  

---

## 3. Children's Privacy  
Our app is designed to be safe for children of all ages. We comply with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) by:  

- Not collecting any personal information from users under 13  
- Not requiring account creation  
- Not featuring any external links or advertisements  

---

## 4. Changes to This Privacy Policy  
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app, and continued use of the app after such changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.  

---

## 5. Contact Us  
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:  

**Email**: bevylabs@gmail.com
